trong>&#8220;) and other applicable legislation on the protection of personal data.</p><p>The purpose of this privacy policy (hereinafter the &#8220;<strong>Privacy Policy</strong>&#8220;) is to describe how the Internet websites listed below in specific sections for each company in the Mondadori Group (hereinafter the &#8220;<strong>Internet websites</strong>“) are managed with reference to the processing of personal data of users/visitors who consult them in accordance with the Regulation.</p><p>In line with applicable regulations, the Mondadori Group intends to guarantee the protection and security of each visitor&#8217;s personal data, also in relation to internet access from abroad, in line with the provisions of this Privacy Policy.</p><p>Unless otherwise specified and regulated by a specific privacy policy issued pursuant to Article 13 of the Regulation, this Privacy Policy shall also be considered as a document intended to provide information pursuant to Articles 13 and 14 of the Regulation to those who browse the Internet Websites and interact with the data controller through the services offered by the Internet Websites.</p><p>It should be noted that this Privacy Policy is applicable solely to Mondadori Group websites and does not refer to other websites that the user may consult in the course of their navigation by clicking on links and/or banners on the Internet Websites.</p><p><strong>2_List of Internet Websites</strong><br/> The following table shows the individual companies that belong to the Mondadori Group and the Internet Websites that refer to each.</p></div> <aside class="col-sm-3  hidden-xs "><div class="js-sticky_column"> <span class="hidden-xs"> <time datetime="2018-05-24 00:00:00">24 May 2018 </time></span></div> </aside></div> </section></div></div></div></div><section class="stripe diag-top-left bg-gray"><div class="container"><table class="table responsive-table entry privacy_policy"><thead><tr><th data-type="html">Soggetto</th><th data-ty